_book":-4.7290516,"book_value":-11.755,"eps_trailing":10.05,"payout_ratio":0.0,"revenue":3013181952.0,"revenue_per_share":130.595,"revenue_growth":0.024,"ebitda":231936000.0,"ebitda_margins":0.07697,"gross_margins":0.28258,"operating_margins":0.03557,"profit_margins":0.07695,"net_income":231874000.0,"total_cash":457700000.0,"total_cash_per_share":19.797,"total_debt":2147500032.0,"enterprise_value":2975000064.0,"enterprise_to_ebitda":12.827,"enterprise_to_revenue":0.987,"earnings_growth":-0.359,"shares_outstanding":23092628.0,"float_shares":7533644.0,"held_pct_insiders":0.63321996,"held_pct_institutions":0.0,"beta":-0.667,"fifty_two_week_high":133.0,"fifty_two_week_low":54.0,"fifty_day_average":69.7554,"two_hundred_day_avg":90.616,"recommendation":"none","all_time_high":133.0,"all_time_low":56.25,"long_business_summary":"Jyoti Limited designs, manufactures, and sells pumps and EPC pumping systems in India. The company offers engineered pumps and projects, including vertical turbine, vertical mixed flow, metallic volute, vertical propeller, horizontal split casing, vertical and horizontal non clog centrifugal, and end suction pumps; and hydel products, such as turbines, inlet valves, and hydro generators. It also provides rotating electrical machines comprising motors, alternators, wind energy and induction generators, Arno and frequency converters, and pole amplitude modulated motors; and switchgears, which include indoor and outdoor vacuum circuit breakers, draw out units, indoor vacuum contractors, retrofits, and ring main units. In addition, the company offers electronic and control systems, such as mini auxiliary relays, pluggable interface miniature auxiliary relays, and general-purpose miniature auxiliary relays. It serves the power generation, transmission, and distribution; irrigation; steel; paper; fertilizer; agriculture water supply and sewerage scheme; railway; cement; sugar; and chemical and petrochemical industries, as well as naval and marine establishments; and public sectors. The company exports its switchgears to the Sultanate of Oman. Jyoti Limited was incorporated in 1943 and is headquartered in Vadodara, India."}}